{"id":346,"parent_id":325,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":346,"title":"2 Kings 21","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Kgs.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 21"],[".studySummary",["i","Manasseh turns Judah to idolatry, even sacrificing a son to a heathen god—Prophets foretell the destruction of Judah and Jerusalem—Wickedness continues under Amon."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.1","order":"02.13.021.27139"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Manasseh"],["i","was"],"twelve years old when he began to reign, and reigned fifty and five years in Jerusalem. And his mother’s name",["i","was"],"Hephzi-bah."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.2","order":"02.13.021.27140"},["b","2"],"And he did",["i","that which was"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"evil"],"in the sight of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", after the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"abominations"],"of the heathen, whom the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"cast out before the children of Israel."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.3","order":"02.13.021.27141"},["b","3"],"For he built up again the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"high places"],"which Hezekiah his father had destroyed; and he reared up altars for Baal, and made a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"grove"],", as did Ahab king of Israel; and worshipped all the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"host"],"of heaven, and served them."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.4","order":"02.13.021.27142"},["b","4"],"And he built",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"altars"],"in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"house"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", of which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said, In Jerusalem will I put my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"name"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.5","order":"02.13.021.27143"},["b","5"],"And he built altars for all the host of heaven in the two",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"courts"],"of the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.6","order":"02.13.021.27144"},["b","6"],"And he made his son pass through the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"fire"],", and observed times, and used",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"enchantments"],", and dealt with",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"familiar spirits"],"and wizards: he wrought much wickedness in the sight of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", to provoke",["i","him"],"to anger."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.7","order":"02.13.021.27145"},["b","7"],"And he set a graven",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"image"],"of the grove that he had made in the house, of which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said to David, and to Solomon his son, In this house, and in Jerusalem, which I have chosen out of all tribes of Israel, will I put my name for ever:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.8","order":"02.13.021.27146"},["b","8"],"Neither will I make the feet of Israel move any more out of the land which I gave their fathers; only if they will observe to do according to all that I have commanded them, and according to all the law that my servant Moses commanded them."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.9","order":"02.13.021.27147"},["b","9"],"But they hearkened not: and Manasseh seduced them to do more",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"evil"],"than did the nations whom the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"destroyed before the children of Israel."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.10","order":"02.13.021.27148"},["b","10"],"¶And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"spake by his servants the prophets, saying,"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.11","order":"02.13.021.27149"},["b","11"],"Because",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Manasseh"],"king of Judah hath done these",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"abominations"],",",["i","and"],"hath done",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"wickedly"],"above all that the Amorites did, which",["i","were"],"before him, and hath made Judah also to sin with his idols:"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.12","order":"02.13.021.27150"},["b","12"],"Therefore thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of Israel, Behold, I",["i","am"],"bringing",["i","such"],"evil upon Jerusalem and Judah, that whosoever heareth of it, both his ears shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"tingle"],"."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.13","order":"02.13.021.27151"},["b","13"],"And I will stretch over Jerusalem the line of Samaria, and the plummet of the house of Ahab: and I will wipe Jerusalem as",["i","a man"],"wipeth a dish, wiping",["i","it,"],"and turning",["i","it"],"upside down."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.14","order":"02.13.021.27152"},["b","14"],"And I will forsake the remnant of mine inheritance, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"deliver"],"them into the hand of their enemies; and they shall become a prey and a spoil to all their enemies;"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.15","order":"02.13.021.27153"},["b","15"],"Because they have done",["i","that which was"],"evil in my sight, and have provoked me to anger, since the day their fathers came forth out of Egypt, even unto this day."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.16","order":"02.13.021.27154"},["b","16"],"Moreover Manasseh",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"shed"],"innocent",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"blood"],"very much, till he had filled Jerusalem from one end to another; beside his sin wherewith he made Judah to sin, in doing",["i","that which was"],"evil in the sight of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.17","order":"02.13.021.27155"},["b","17"],"¶Now the rest of the acts of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"Manasseh"],", and all that he did, and his sin that he sinned,",["i","are"],"they not written in the book of the chronicles of the kings of Judah?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.18","order":"02.13.021.27156"},["b","18"],"And Manasseh slept with his fathers, and was buried in the garden of his own house, in the garden of Uzza: and Amon his son reigned in his stead."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.19","order":"02.13.021.27157"},["b","19"],"¶",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Amon"],["i","was"],"twenty and two years old when he began to reign, and he reigned two years in Jerusalem. And his mother’s name",["i","was"],"Meshullemeth, the daughter of Haruz of Jotbah."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.20","order":"02.13.021.27158"},["b","20"],"And he did",["i","that which was"],"evil in the sight of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", as his father Manasseh did."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.21","order":"02.13.021.27159"},["b","21"],"And he walked in all the way that his father walked in, and served the idols that his father served, and worshipped them:"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.22","order":"02.13.021.27160"},["b","22"],"And he forsook the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of his fathers, and walked not in the way of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.23","order":"02.13.021.27161"},["b","23"],"¶And the servants of Amon conspired against him, and slew the king in his own house."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.24","order":"02.13.021.27162"},["b","24"],"And the people of the land slew all them that had conspired against king Amon; and the people of the land made",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"Josiah"],"his son king in his stead."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.25","order":"02.13.021.27163"},["b","25"],"Now the rest of the acts of Amon which he did,",["i","are"],"they not written in the book of the chronicles of the kings of Judah?"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.26","order":"02.13.021.27164"},["b","26"],"And he was buried in his sepulchre in the garden of Uzza: and Josiah his son reigned in his stead."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.1a","order":"02.13.021.27165"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/33.1.1-20"},"2 Chr. 33:1 (1–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.2a","order":"02.13.021.27167"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sin"},"TG Sin"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.2b","order":"02.13.021.27169"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.3a","order":"02.13.021.27171"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/18.4"},"2 Kgs. 18:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.3b","order":"02.13.021.27173"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/16.33.32-33"},"1 Kgs. 16:33 (32–33)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.3c","order":"02.13.021.27175"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/17.16.15-17"},"2 Kgs. 17:16 (15–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.4a","order":"02.13.021.27177"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/7.30.29-31"},"Jer. 7:30 (29–31)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idolatry"},"TG Idolatry"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.4b","order":"02.13.021.27179"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/23.39"},"Ezek. 23:39"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.4c","order":"02.13.021.27181"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/8.29"},"1 Kgs. 8:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/9.3.1-4"},"9:3 (1–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.5a","order":"02.13.021.27183"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.36"},"1 Kgs. 6:36"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/7.12"},"7:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.6a","order":"02.13.021.27185"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/18.21"},"Lev. 18:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/28.3"},"2 Chr. 28:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/33.6"},"33:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/20.26"},"Ezek. 20:26"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/superstitions"},"TG Superstitions"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.6b","order":"02.13.021.27187"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/19.26"},"Lev. 19:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.6c","order":"02.13.021.27189"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-evil-or-unclean"},"TG Spirits, Evil or Unclean"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.7a","order":"02.13.021.27191"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idolatry"},"TG Idolatry"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.9a","order":"02.13.021.27193"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/tyranny"},"TG Tyranny"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.11a","order":"02.13.021.27195"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/15.4"},"Jer. 15:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.11b","order":"02.13.021.27197"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/24.3.3-4"},"2 Kgs. 24:3 (3–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.11c","order":"02.13.021.27199"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/21.26"},"1 Kgs. 21:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/23.26"},"2 Kgs. 23:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.12a","order":"02.13.021.27201"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.11"},"1 Sam. 3:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.3"},"Jer. 19:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.14a","order":"02.13.021.27203"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/24.2"},"2 Kgs. 24:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.16a","order":"02.13.021.27205"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/24.4"},"2 Kgs. 24:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.16b","order":"02.13.021.27207"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/blood-shedding-of"},"TG Blood, Shedding of"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.17a","order":"02.13.021.27209"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/33.18.11-19"},"2 Chr. 33:18 (11–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.19a","order":"02.13.021.27211"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/33.21.21-25"},"2 Chr. 33:21 (21–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.24a","order":"02.13.021.27213"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.1"},"Zeph. 1:1"],"."]]}
